{"tid":1094983,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣健康調味料","createTime":"2019-04-06T16:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T17:39:45.000Z","uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d099f922128d6047da84cf41275f136baa91505a","tid":1094983,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"小弟身子唔太好<br />\n所以喺屋企食飯都比較少用豉油蠔油呢啲調味<br />\n但有時煮餸只係落鹽又好寡<br />\n咁多位巴絲有冇健康有益調味好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6244b74f23cac7fbdef4fa966a09b76eb931b9ab","tid":1094983,"uid":106326,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:58:39.000Z","msg":"蔥 洋蔥 蒜 糖<br />\n<br />\n仲有其實豉油同蠔油呢啲都唔係啲咩好唔健康既野<br />\n搞咁多不如做多啲運動<br />\n或者飲食習慣好啲"},{"pid":"1e4171df98872573d01f74575d8d1577fcc0222b","tid":1094983,"uid":158103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"冬菇粉?"},{"pid":"066ca2a7d8944a7369510290bc5acadc765326f3","tid":1094983,"uid":217674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:59:42.000Z","msg":"美極"},{"pid":"da8f54b5f6ffed5afc287d3e4589128645bd49d4","tid":1094983,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6244b74f23cac7fbdef4fa966a09b76eb931b9ab","tid":1094983,"uid":106326,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:58:39.000Z","msg":"蔥 洋蔥 蒜 糖<br />\n<br />\n仲有其實豉油同蠔油呢啲都唔係啲咩好唔健康既野<br />\n搞咁多不如做多啲運動<br />\n或者飲食習慣好啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"就係想雙管齊下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de481138b7b77291f22057f3554646daebc2face","tid":1094983,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e4171df98872573d01f74575d8d1577fcc0222b","tid":1094983,"uid":158103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"冬菇粉?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:02:37.000Z","msg":"好似唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"